          "year": 2024,
          "note": "Started life as a Disney+ series before the studio turned it into a theatrical feature, with a new directing team and Abigail Barlow and Emily Bear replacing Lin-Manuel Miranda on songs. Sean finds it a disappointing McGuffin hunt that maps too cleanly onto the first film; the kids in the theater loved it anyway."
        },
        {
          "title": "Moana",
          "year": 2016,
          "note": "The Musker-and-Clements original Sean rates as about as good as Disney animation gets. Yasi rewatched it to pregame and cried against her will."
